{"sections":[],"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSToolBarTop"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents14OUDSToolBarTopV","platforms":[{"introducedAt":"15.0","unavailable":false,"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"iOS"},{"introducedAt":"1.0","unavailable":false,"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"visionOS"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","symbolKind":"struct","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSToolBarTop"}],"title":"OUDSToolBarTop"},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudstoolbartop"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSToolBarTop\/init(title:hasLargeTitle:subtitle:leadingItems:trailingItems:)"],"title":"Initializers","generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSToolBarTop\/body(content:)"],"title":"Instance Methods","generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Methods"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSToolBarTop\/ViewModifier-Implementations"],"title":"Default Implementations","generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI12ViewModifierP"],"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSToolBarTop"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"toolBarTop(_:hasLargeTitle:subtitle:leadingItems:trailingItems:)"},{"text":"  View helper applies a SwiftUI toolbar configuration.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Appearances","type":"heading","text":"Appearances"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"With Liquid Glass \/ iOS 26+ the OS will change the rendering of the toolbar items depending to the context:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The OS can group the items of same types in one group with kind of rectangle (e.g. views with menus)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"But for buttons items they will remain isolated","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The placement of the title can be leading or centered depending to the length of the text","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The text can be truncated if there is not enough remaining space","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The OS can apply another style for the back button","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Without Liquid Glass \/ iOS 18 and lower, the OS won’t change that much the style of the toolbar items, Items won’t be visually grouped.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Globaly the appearence of the * navigation bar* elements is changed by the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"oudsNavigationBarAppearance"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"helper of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"text":" that must be applyed on the root view of the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NavigationStack"},{"text":" for example.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Technical-constraints","type":"heading","text":"Technical constraints"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To be sure for iOS 18 and lower the back buttton and text have the good color, in your main view apply the following accent color:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    struct AppMainView: View {","        var body: some View {","            ContentView()","                .accentColor(theme.colors.contentDefault)","        }","    }"]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Platform-considerations","type":"heading","text":"Platform considerations"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The component is available on iOS, iPadOS, and visionOS","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The component is not available for watchOS, tvOS and macOS","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Badges-uses","type":"heading","text":"Badges uses"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For iOS 26 with Liquid Glass, the system badge is used because the OUDS badge component does not provide a suitable","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"rendering with the glassified effect applied on the top toolbar.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"For iOS until 18 and without Liquid Glass  OUDS badge component is always used.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Code-sample","type":"heading","text":"Code sample"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    ContentView()","        .toolBarTop(\"Title\",","            leadingItems: {","                OUDSToolBarItem(navigation: .back())","            },","            trailingItems: {","                OUDSToolBarItem(label: \"Label\") { \/* Action to process *\/ }","                OUDSToolBarItem(icon: Image(decorative: \"some_image\"), accessibilityLabel: \"Label\") { \/* Action to process *\/ }","            }","        )"]},{"level":2,"anchor"